snippet.title: JetX Space Edition Trailer  (No VR edition)
snippet.description:
Fastest VR game now on PC

One minute of extremely dynamic JetX gameplay. Excite your brain with colors!

Don't forget to add us in Steam wishlist: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/684620/JetX/

We're waiting for you in our Discord chat to discuss the plan of the race: https://discord.gg/uhvKYF

Also, be sure to join any other JetX social network:
facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JetXvr/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/JetX_VR
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCupQkXYEdVwG_cHPS1KVn3w
reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/JetX/

Published by Fibrum
